{"tid":2362920,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"波蘭政府開始調查監督CDPR對2077的承諾","createTime":"2021-01-11T21:31:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T01:49:18.000Z","uid":14812,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a63e107485d9f9e3395fd3039c5d1c787701ee1d","tid":2362920,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T21:31:52.000Z","msg":"波蘭政府底下的&quot;商業競爭及消費者保護辦公室(UOKiK)&quot; 開始監督CDPR<br />\n <br />\n辦公室發言人說 CDPR 必須要準時推出之前承諾家機消費者的 patch<br />\n <br />\n除了 CDPR 要定期跟波蘭政府回報開發進度外<br />\n <br />\n如果最後 CDPR 食言 承諾的東西沒準時做出來的話<br />\n <br />\n辦公室主席有權力罰錢 最多可以罰 CDPR 去年年營收 10%<br />\n <br />\n可預期會給2077開發團隊更大壓力<br />\n <br />\n波蘭政府曾投資700萬美金給CDPR研發新遊戲技術<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n來源:<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/39oLJH3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F39oLJH3&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BT4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=8c3484d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/39oLJH3</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3sgeFcD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3sgeFcD&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BT4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=819add3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3sgeFcD</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2LoyAFH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2LoyAFH&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BT4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=25b98259\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2LoyAFH</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://moptt.tw/p/PlayStation.M.1610345848.A.8C6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoptt.tw%2Fp%2FPlayStation.M.1610345848.A.8C6&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BT4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=8ec106b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://moptt.tw/p/PlayStation.M.1610345848.A.8C6</a>"},{"pid":"d503fd9b4823c648cba186874209f1faa0abf748","tid":2362920,"uid":130568,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T22:07:42.000Z","msg":"高層垃圾一日唔改，定啲deadline出嚟等於玩死developer"},{"pid":"a2048b78a24218645c6483e36578329755d878b9","tid":2362920,"uid":117301,"like":4,"di